headline: Allergan Aesthetics Offers Free Business Education Courses Online to Support Growing Practices with Allergan Aesthetics Products
summary: Allergan Aesthetics, an AbbVie company, launched AMI Business Education, a new addition to the AMI Online learning platform available for free to all Allergan Aesthetics customers. This innovative offering empowers healthcare practitioners, their staff, and management with business education practices focused on Allergan Aesthetics products to enhance patient service and achieve operational excellence.

headline: Why This Beaten-Down Dividend Stock Is a No-Brainer Buy on the Dip
summary: Last year, pharmaceutical giant AbbVie (NYSE: ABBV) lost patent exclusivity for its biggest cash cow, immunology medicine Humira.  The drugmaker has rebounded quite nicely since.  AbbVie returned to top-line growth in the second quarter, much earlier than many anticipated.

headline: AbbVie Receives European Commission Approval of ELAHERE® (mirvetuximab soravtansine) for the Treatment of Platinum-Resistant Ovarian Cancer
summary: AbbVie (NYSE: ABBV) today announced the European Commission (EC) granted marketing authorization for ELAHERE® (mirvetuximab soravtansine) for the treatment of adult patients with folate receptor-alpha (FRα) positive, platinum-resistant high grade serous epithelial ovarian, fallopian tube or primary peritoneal cancer who have received one to three prior systemic treatment regimens.
